Rapper Flames who recently had a fall out with Areece lost his cool on stage. This is after he threw a warm Klaap to a fan who threw alcohol at him.  The drama took place in the full view of other party patrons, a video making rounds shows an angry Flame angrily manhandling the fan before moering him with a warm klaap. Flame who then took to social media after being called out started swearing at fans in now deleted tweets.  